      "hypothesis": "Holder threshold sweep - second-tightest. Cuts the bottom ~10-12% of the universe (<18 holders). Note: in the v25-bot-excl-climbing loss-postmortem, 2 of 20 worst losers had holder_count=18 (grad 23674 -90.2% and grad 23552 -65.2%). Filtering at >=18 would have kept those losers - so this threshold's discrimination is largely in the 'background' trade population, not at the loss tail. Useful comparison point against >=19.",
